Further information
POSITION SUMMARY:
To provide a courteous, professional, efficient and flexible Food and Beverage Service consistent with Holiday Inn Dubai Al Barsha  standards, in order to maximize guest satisfaction.
To perform duties and responsibilities in a safe manner.
To take responsibility for individual development and acquire minimum levels of knowledge, skills and/or abilities. To perform this job successfully, the incumbent will possess the abilities or aptitudes to perform each duty proficiently.
To actively promote the services and facilities of Holiday Inn Dubai Al Barsha to guests, visitors and suppliers of the Hotel.
Record order of guest following departmental policies and sequence of service
Greet guests upon arrival at the outlet and assist in seating in accordance with departmental standards and sequence of service
Take guest’s beverage order, utilizing suggestive selling techniques, when specified on function requirements
Retrieve alcoholic beverage items from bar and serve to guest in accordance with the departmental standards
Open and serve wine /champagne bottles in front of the guest in accordance to the standard
Holiday Inn Dubai - Al Barsha
It is our people, who make the difference and provide genuinely caring service to our guests, and why our guests keep returning to Holiday Inn Dubai – Al Barsha
